'''Léon Konan Koffi''' (16 November 1928 – 29 August 2017)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.connectionivoirienne.net/128971/cote-divoire-lex-ministre-dhouphouet-leon-konan-koffi-est-mort|title=Côte d’Ivoire: L’ex-ministre d’Houphouët Léon Konan Koffi est mort|website=Connectionivoirienne.net|accessdate=31 August 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.linfodrome.com/vie-politique/33551-le-pdci-encore-en-deuil-le-dernier-ministre-de-la-defense-d-houphouet-est-decede|title=Deuil : Léon Konan Koffi, ancien ministre de la Défense d'Houphouët est décédé|first=Félix D.|last=Bony|date=29 August 2017|website=Linfodrome.com|accessdate=31 August 2017}}</ref> was an Ivorian politician. He served as the Interior Minister of the [[Ivory Coast]] under President [[Félix Houphouët-Boigny]].<ref name="fraternitematinobit">{{cite news|last1=Koffi|first1=Michel|title=Hommage à Léon Konan Koffi: Il murmurait à l’oreille de Félix Houphouët-Boigny|url=https://www.fratmat.info/index.php/politique/hommage-a-leon-konan-koffi-il-murmurait-a-l-oreille-de-felix-houphouet-boigny|accessdate=31 August 2017|work=[[Fraternité Matin]]|date=31 August 2017}}</ref> He was a commander of the [[National Order of Merit (France)|National Order of Merit]] and the [[Legion of Honour]].<ref name="fraternitematinobit"/>
