'''''Nessy Learning Programme''''' is an interactive, multi-media [[computer program]], used in UK Primary Schools, that enables dyslexic students between 5 and 16 years to read, write and spell with confidence. It was developed and published by [[Net Educational Systems]] - now known as [https://www.nessy.com Nessy.]

