=== Foreign relations of Åland ===
* Although autonomous, Åland is part of Finland and does not conduct foreign relations. ** [[Åland (constituency)|Åland as a constituency of Finland]] ** [[Åland convention]]s &mdash; establish the demilitarization and neutralization of Åland. * [[Special Member State territories and the European Union#Åland Islands|Relationship of Åland to the European Union]] &mdash; Åland is a Special Member of the EU.
