=== Military of Åland ===
* [[Military of Åland|Military status of Åland]] &mdash; Åland is both demilitarized and neutralized by international treaty: it may not militarize, be militarized, nor participate in war. ** [[Åland crisis]] ** [[Åland convention]]s &mdash; establish the demilitarization and neutralization of Åland. ** Command *** [[Commander-in-chief]]: none *** Ministry of Defence: none ** Conscription in Åland &mdash; Citizens of Åland cannot be [[Conscription|conscripted]] into military service. * Forces: none * Military bases: none
