[[File:Quartiers de Novi Sad - Sremska Kamenica.png|thumb|250px|Map of the urban area of Novi Sad with city quarters, showing the location of Popovica within Sremska Kamenica]]
'''Popovica''' ([[Cyrillic]]: Поповица) is a small neighborhood of [[Sremska Kamenica]], [[Serbia]].{{r|"Moser2016"}} It is located on the edge of the urban area of [[Novi Sad]] and [[Fruška Gora|National Park of Fruška Gora]].{{r|"Balašević1966"}} Popovica is connected to Sremska Kamenica and Novi Sad by public bus No.74.
It is also the name of a Mountain Peak [[Popovica (peak)]].

