'''Serbia''' selected their [[Junior Eurovision Song Contest 2014]] entry through an internal selection. On 1 October 2014 it was revealed that [[Emilija Đonin]] would represent Serbia in the contest with the song "[[Svet u mojim očima]]".<ref name="Serbia1">{{cite web|title=Listen to Emilija Djonin's "Svet u mojim očima"|url=http://www.junioreurovision.tv/page/blog?id=listen_to_emilija_djonins_svet_u_mojim_ocima|last=Juhász|first=Ervin|publisher=EBU|accessdate=1 October 2014|date=1 October 2014}}</ref>
==Internal selection== On 1 October 2014, it was revealed that the [[Serbia]]n teen singer [[Emilija Đonin]], would represent Serbia with the song "Svet u mojim očima".<ref name="Serbia1"/>
