{{unref|date=February 2017}}
The '''Sly River''' is a [[river]] in northern [[Algeria]], [[North Africa]].
The Sly River is a tributary of the [[Chelif]] [[River]] and joins the Chelif just east of the town of [[Sidi ben Thiour]].

